caption.p: Celgosivir does not alter activated caspase 3/7 levels in CHME3 cells infected with Zika virus (ZIKV). Luminescence measurements of activated caspase 3/7 from CHME3 cells 48 (A) and 72 (B) hours following infection with ZIKV PRVABC59 with and without celgosivir. Data points represents mean luminescence of four biological replicates with error bars showing standard deviation.
